    "created_at": "2016-03-29T18:47:10Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-03-29T18:47:10Z",
    "body": "It's funny because I've been trying to solve why Chromium disables RequestAnimationFrame when we minimize, but it doesn't when we use WindowsKey+D.  Which is a good thing in my case because my game is multiplayer and I need RAF to be running 24/7.   So using the setMinimizable option fixes that for me, but I hope it stays and doesn't turn into a bug and get's patched later down the road :(\n"
